Description:
    Creates an rwt application. An rwt application is an initial page that
    creates the environment to execute and show the 'views' to
    be sent to the browser/client by the rails application/server.
    This initial page will tipically show a menu to start the various 'views'
    of the rwt application.

    Pass the name of the controller, either CamelCased or under_scored, as the first
    argument,


Prerequisites:
		You need to download the Ext Javascript framework from

		`http://extjs.com/download`,

		and unzip it into `#{RAILS_ROOT}/public/ext`. Rwt_application was
		tested against version 3.0.0 of the Ext framework.

Examples:
    `./script/generate rwt_application desktop`
